        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages, <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.conditionitems\" data-id=\"kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei\"> Grabs</a>, or <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"PMbdMWc2QroouFGD\"> Grapples</a> your ally, and both are within 15 feet of you</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You free an ally from <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.conditionitems\" data-id=\"VcDeM8A5oI6VqhbM\"> Restraint</a>. If the trigger was an ally taking damage, the ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to 2 + your level. The ally can attempt to break free of effects grabbing, restraining, <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.conditionitems\" data-id=\"eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe\"> Immobilizing</a>, or <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.conditionitems\" data-id=\"6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF\"> Paralyzing</a> them. They either attempt a new save against one such effect that allows a save, or attempt to <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"SkZAQRkLLkmBQNB9\"> Escape</a> from one effect as a free action. If they can move, the ally can Step as a free action, even if they didn't need to escape.</p>"
